$PAR
For the following, write out each term of the
summation in the boxes provided.  Then compute
the sum.
$PAR
a) \(\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{5} \dfrac{1}{i} \) 
= \{ans_rule(5)\} \(+\) \{ans_rule(5)\} \(+\) \{ans_rule(5)\}
\(+\) \{ans_rule(5)\} \(+\) \{ans_rule(5)\}  
\( = \) \{ans_rule(10)\}
$HR
$PAR
