= \{ans_rule(5)\} \(+\) \{ans_rule(5)\} \(+\) \{ans_rule(5)\}
\(+\) \{ans_rule(5)\} \(+\) \{ans_rule(5)\}  \(+\) \{ans_rule(5)\}
\( = \) \{ans_rule(10)\}
$HR
$PAR
c) \(\displaystyle\sum_{i=1}^{4}\left( \dfrac{1}{i} - \dfrac{1}{i+1} 
